{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-chapter-level-2-chapter-level-2-tsx","path":"/topics/obstructive-sleep-apnoea-syndrome/background-information/risk-factors/","result":{"pageContext":{"chapter":{"id":"889500de-7900-591d-a514-d06d22717f01","slug":"risk-factors","fullItemName":"Risk factors","depth":2,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field d5a2037a-4585-4497-9478-f289a0051a81 --><h2>What are the risk factors?</h2><!-- end field d5a2037a-4585-4497-9478-f289a0051a81 -->","summary":"","htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item 46f8b30f-2fbc-4b5a-a648-b3ce27c51af5 --><!-- begin field 0bffa33b-337a-494e-8775-e9469d5e4032 --><ul><li><strong>Risk factors for developing obstructive sleep apnoea syndrome (OSAS) in </strong><strong>adults include:</strong><ul><li>Male sex (the male to female ratio is 2–3:1).</li><li>Obesity.</li><li>Neck circumference greater than 43 cm.</li><li>Family history of OSAS.</li><li>Smoking.</li><li>Alcohol intake before bed.</li><li>Sleeping supine.</li><li>Hypothyroidism.</li><li>Craniofacial abnormalities.</li><li>Acromegaly.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Risk factors for OSAS in children include:</strong><ul><li>Adenotonsillar hypertrophy.</li><li>Obesity.</li><li>Congenital conditions (such as Down's syndrome, neuromuscular disease, craniofacial abnormalities, achondroplasia, and Prader–Willi syndrome).</li></ul></li></ul><p>[<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/obstructive-sleep-apnoea-syndrome/references/\">SIGN, 2003</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/obstructive-sleep-apnoea-syndrome/references/\">NICE, 2008</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/obstructive-sleep-apnoea-syndrome/references/\">Punjabi, 2008</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/obstructive-sleep-apnoea-syndrome/references/\">Powell et al, 2010</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/obstructive-sleep-apnoea-syndrome/references/\">Powell, 2011</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/obstructive-sleep-apnoea-syndrome/references/\">Smith and Quinnell, 2011</a>]</p><!-- end field 0bffa33b-337a-494e-8775-e9469d5e4032 --><!-- end item 46f8b30f-2fbc-4b5a-a648-b3ce27c51af5 -->","topic":{"id":"f1196501-9004-50dc-b7d4-52b757fd68f1","topicId":"f39c3a30-1d8b-4e7f-b393-c9630f5cc63e","topicName":"Obstructive sleep apnoea syndrome","slug":"obstructive-sleep-apnoea-syndrome","lastRevised":"Last revised in April 2015","chapters":[{"id":"bc5b27b2-fcc2-5d5f-9226-645ee30f74c0","fullItemName":"Summary","slug":"summary","subChapters":[]},{"id":"6f088cf7-eb48-5367-8924-56f6b7bc8a09","fullItemName":"Have I got the right topic?","slug":"have-i-got-the-right-topic","subChapters":[]},{"id":"038fcffa-9056-5240-9299-e41f1639e4a7","fullItemName":"How up-to-date is this topic?","slug":"how-up-to-date-is-this-topic","subChapters":[{"id":"1a571c23-537f-5a82-a38a-7c305b7fa5f4","slug":"changes","fullItemName":"Changes"},{"id":"cb715fc0-8cc6-5416-9b8a-2ec368695d99","slug":"update","fullItemName":"Update"}]},{"id":"b94c615c-9c1f-52cb-8763-a12b7d8d9625","fullItemName":"Goals and outcome measures","slug":"goals-outcome-measures","subChapters":[{"id":"2828f216-104e-5fb3-b1c2-1606b4c53a01","slug":"goals","fullItemName":"Goals"},{"id":"6866a745-4dd4-5d8c-bde9-b0abc2f8025e","slug":"outcome-measures","fullItemName":"Outcome measures"},{"id":"8850177a-a107-5b41-b1ab-8a23a444206f","slug":"audit-criteria","fullItemName":"Audit criteria"},{"id":"342ff900-c46b-54f4-a039-e89370f103c2","slug":"qof-indicators","fullItemName":"QOF indicators"},{"id":"3be809f8-22d2-54ec-a6b6-3e5b481e9aed","slug":"qipp-options-for-local-implementation","fullItemName":"QIPP - Options for local implementation"},{"id":"8bfaf481-5c93-519b-a00b-54a6d720ad8a","slug":"nice-quality-standards","fullItemName":"NICE quality standards"}]},{"id":"ea06b8c9-e520-5542-a8aa-9ed114071eae","fullItemName":"Background